 "lrc": "[00:00.80]Yeah\n[00:01.44]Uh\n[00:04.32]Summer night, laptop glow\n[00:07.12]Little ice in the glass\n[00:09.84]We working different now\n[00:11.04]Come on\n[00:11.28]Ooh, cocktails and code\n[00:12.64]Ooh, watch the new me load\n[00:18.08]Ooh, we don’t move like before\n[00:24.40]No, no, no\n[00:28.64]Sunset dripping through the blinds like gold\n[00:33.68]Same little room but the dream got bold\n[00:36.16]Glass on the table with the ice half low\n[00:38.24]Got my mind on fire and my laptop glow\n[00:40.96]I used to scroll when the day went dead\n[00:43.20]Same old worries running loops in my head\n[00:45.60]Now I open up a new tab, breathe in slow\n[00:48.32]Type one question and the whole world grows\n[00:50.72]I ain’t tryna flex like I know it all\n[00:52.88]I just stopped waiting on a miracle call\n[00:55.60]One small build, one clean plan\n[00:58.00]One more skill in the palm of my hand\n[01:00.16]AI talking, I’m talking back\n[01:02.56]Turning little ideas into something that lasts\n[01:05.20]Summer breeze coming through the screen\n[01:07.28]Feels like palm trees living in the machine\n[01:10.16]Mix a little focus with the moonlight\n[01:13.04]Add a little rhythm to the grind\n[01:15.04]We don’t have to run from the daylight\n[01:17.44]We can make a way this time\n[01:19.84]Cocktails and code\n[01:21.20]That’s how the night unfolds\n[01:22.88]Got a little dream in the glass\n[01:24.64]Got a little fire in the soul\n[01:29.20]Cocktails and code\n[01:30.64]Watch the new me load\n[01:31.92]I can feel that future getting closer\n[01:34.40]Every time I take control\n[01:38.24]Sip, sip, type it up\n[01:41.36]Build, build, level up\n[01:42.24]No more waiting on the world\n[01:43.52]We gon’ make it come to us\n[01:44.88]Cocktails and code\n[01:46.72]That’s how the night unfolds\n[01:48.96]Summer in my source code\n[01:50.24]Watch the new me load\n[01:54.48]Na na na, let it run\n[01:56.32]Na na na, here we come\n[01:56.32]Na na na, don’t you know\n[01:56.32]Cocktails and code\n[01:56.32]I used to think the good life had a gate\n[01:56.48]Somebody at the front saying wait, wait, wait\n[01:59.20]Now I see the lock got a pattern to it\n[02:01.36]Learn a little logic, put some action through it\n[02:03.52]Debug my doubt, clean up my days\n[02:05.92]Automate the noise, let the stress drift away\n[02:08.32]Build me a page, build me a flow\n[02:10.72]Build me a bridge where the old me won’t go\n[02:13.36]It ain’t magic, but it feel like that\n[02:15.44]When the idea hits and the beat comes back\n[02:17.92]Bassline walking like it knows my name\n[02:20.56]808 snap like a champagne frame\n[02:22.56]I want beach chairs paid from the things I made\n[02:24.96]Not another short break that I barely saved\n[02:27.44]I want Monday soft, I want time that’s mine\n[02:29.60]I want sunlight sitting on a better design\n[02:31.84]Mix a little focus with the moonlight\n[02:35.20]Add a little rhythm to the grind\n[02:37.44]We don’t have to run from the daylight\n[02:39.84]We can make a way this time\n[02:42.24]Cocktails and code\n[02:43.60]That’s how the night unfolds\n[02:45.28]Got a little dream in the glass\n[02:47.12]Got a little fire in the soul\n[02:51.60]Cocktails and code\n[02:53.28]Watch the new me load\n[02:54.72]I can feel that future getting closer\n[02:56.80]Every time I take control\n[03:00.64]Sip, sip, type it up\n[03:03.44]Build, build, level up\n[03:04.72]No more waiting on the world\n[03:05.92]We gon’ make it come to us\n[03:07.36]Cocktails and code\n[03:09.12]That’s how the night unfolds\n[03:11.04]Summer in my source code\n[03:13.84]Watch the new me load\n[03:16.08]Maybe the beach ain’t far away\n[03:18.64]Maybe it starts with what I make\n[03:21.04]Maybe the life I used to chase\n[03:23.36]Is hiding in the habits I create\n[03:26.24]No more wishing on the Wi-Fi\n[03:28.64]No more waiting for the right sky\n[03:31.04]I got rhythm, I got time\n[03:33.52]I got something on my mind\n[03:35.60]Yeah\n[03:35.60]Prompt me a plan,